you beat two boys.

00:02:44.197 --> 00:02:48.067 line:95%,end
And on top of the pyramid again is Nia.

00:02:48.134 --> 00:02:49.969 line:95%,end
(cheering)

00:02:50.036 --> 00:02:51.804 line:95%,end
ABBY:
Nia, it doesn't always have to do

00:02:51.871 --> 00:02:54.207 line:95%,end
with the dancing and the performance.

00:02:54.274 --> 00:02:57.010 line:95%,end
It has to do with all the other stuff
that goes into it.

00:02:57.076 --> 00:02:59.712 line:95%,end
Abby, Kendall deserves
to be on that pyramid.

00:02:59.779 --> 00:03:02.916 line:95%,end
