three weeks ago before we started.

00:03:12.592 --> 00:03:13.459 line:95%,end
Why?

00:03:13.526 --> 00:03:15.795 line:5%,start
Once again,
Jill got a little spicy with me.

00:03:15.862 --> 00:03:19.132 line:95%,end
Why does she think she can just
walk back into my dance studio

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:21.568 line:95%,end
and get her kid
back on the competition team?

00:03:21.634 --> 00:03:22.735 line:95%,end
<i>You walked out.</i>

00:03:22.802 --> 00:03:24.204 line:95%,end
<i>You went to my enemy.</i>

00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:26.139 line:95%,end
You're going
to have to beg, Jill.

00:03:26.206 --> 00:03:28.274 line:95%,end
She wins
every number you put her in,

00:03:28.341 --> 00:03:29.943 line:95%,end
but she's not on the team.


00:03:30.009 --> 00:03:31.578 line:95%,end
I don't know
what else to do, honey.

00:03:31.644 --> 00:03:34.314 line:95%,end
I'm sorry, because I would not
have put you through this.

00:03:34.380 --> 00:03:35.615 line:95%,end
Putting her through what?

00:03:35.682 --> 00:03:37.550 line:95%,end
She just went
to a competition and won her duet.

00:03:37.617 --> 00:03:39.852 line:95%,end
She learned something.
She was fabulous.

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:42.388 line:95%,end
JILL: She's a winner,
but you still won't put her on the team.

00:03:42.455 --> 00:03:45.692 line:95%,end
The team part,
that's about commitment.

00:03:46.993 --> 00:03:49.028 line:95%,end
And your mother's
always ready to jump ship,

00:03:49.095 --> 00:03:50.697 line:95%,end
just like she was just now.

00:03:50.763 --> 00:03:52.098 line:95%,end
Understood?

00:03:52.165 --> 00:03:54.834 line:95%,end
I'm going to tell everybody
in this room right now,

00:03:54.901 --> 00:03:57.837 line:95%,end
I don't want any altercations.

00:03:57.904 --> 00:03:59.205 line:95%,end
I don't want tears.

00:03:59.272 --> 00:04:01.307 line:95%,end
I don't want screaming, yelling.

00:04:01.374 --> 00:04:03.409 line:95%,end
This is a very big week.

00:04:03.476 --> 00:04:06.813 line:95%,end
We are doing the 2012

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:09.582 line:95%,end
Abby Lee Dance Company concert.

00:04:09.649 --> 00:04:13.419 line:95%,end
It is not a competition,
but it is equally important.

00:04:13.486 --> 00:04:15.722 line:95%,end
This is our opportunity
to showcase

00:04:15.788 --> 00:04:18.091 line:95%,end
all of the dancers in the studio.

00:04:18.157 --> 00:04:20.159 line:95%,end
<i>They get to perform</i>
<i>all of the routines</i>

00:04:20.226 --> 00:04:22.462 line:95%,end
<i>that they've competed</i>
<i>throughout the season.</i>

00:04:22.528 --> 00:04:26.232 line:95%,end
The concert is also
a great opportunity for me

00:04:26.299 --> 00:04:29.035 line:95%,end
to market my studio
to the general public.

00:04:29.102 --> 00:04:31.204 line:95%,end
Hey, I'm trying to get
new students out of this.

00:04:31.271 --> 00:04:33.239 line:95%,end
We are going to be doing a routine.

00:04:33.306 --> 00:04:36.142 line:95%,end
The routine is called
"Light My Fire,"

00:04:36.209 --> 00:04:39.445 line:95%,end
and it's hip-hop.

00:04:39.512 --> 00:04:41.581 line:95%,end
MADDIE: <i>This week</i>
<i>our group dance is hip-hop,</i>

00:04:41.648 --> 00:04:43.416 line:5%,start
and I'm really excited.

00:04:43.483 --> 00:04:46.252 line:5%,start
But none of us can hip or hop.

00:04:46.319 --> 00:04:48.788 line:95%,end
ABBY: Now, Paige, it's been weeks.

00:04:48.855 --> 00:04:51.357 line:95%,end
I think that you are capable

00:04:51.424 --> 00:04:53.893 line:95%,end
of performing in this hip-hop routine.

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:55.928 line:95%,end
KLLY: She has to get approved
by the doctor first.

00:04:55.995 --> 00:04:56.996 line:95%,end
ABBY: Absolutely.

00:04:57.063 --> 00:04:59.299 line:95%,end
But it's going
to be with the boot on.

00:04:59.365 --> 00:05:00.967 line:5%,start
I got strict instructions
from the doctor

00:05:01.034 --> 00:05:04.604 line:5%,start
that she is to do
no dancing until four weeks.

00:05:04.671 --> 00:05:06.372 line:95%,end
We still have
another week to go.

00:05:06.439 --> 00:05:08.007 line:95%,end
ABBY: Kelly, you're an original member

00:05:08.074 --> 00:05:09.142 line:95%,end
of the Abby Lee Dance Company.

00:05:09.208 --> 00:05:12.412 line:95%,end
I would like to see
some of your classmates at the show.

00:05:13.446 --> 00:05:15.982 line:95%,end
My God, I haven't seen them
in 20-some years.

00:05:16.049 --> 00:05:18.985 line:95%,end
ABBY: I want those people
to see that the Abby Lee Dance Company

00:05:19.052 --> 00:05:21.921 line:95%,end
is alive and healthy and strong

00:05:21.988 --> 00:05:24.057 line:95%,end
and continuing
to educate children.

00:05:24.123 --> 00:05:25.091 line:95%,end
Okay.

00:05:25.158 --> 00:05:27.093 line:95%,end
ABBY: Now, there's something else
we're doing.

00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:32.098 line:95%,end
There will be one person
chosen from each age level

00:05:32.165 --> 00:05:35.435 line:95%,end
to win a very generous
cash scholarship.

00:05:35.501 --> 00:05:38.504 line:95%,end
<i>This is the very first time</i>
<i>that the Abby Lee Dance Company</i>

00:05:38.571 --> 00:05:41.507 line:95%,end
<i>Parents Association</i>
<i>has been in the position</i>

00:05:41.574 --> 00:05:45.378 line:95%,end
to give out scholarships
to continue their dance studies.

00:05:45.445 --> 00:05:47.146 line:95%,end
All right, ladies,
you're dismissed.

00:05:47.213 --> 00:05:48.214 line:95%,end
Girls, spread apart.

00:05:48.281 --> 00:05:49.882 line:95%,end
