this number right now.

00:05:49.949 --> 00:05:53.519 line:5%,start
One, two, three.

00:05:53.586 --> 00:05:56.923 line:5%,start
I want everyone in the audience
to realize that these girls

00:05:56.989 --> 00:05:58.224 line:95%,end
can do it all.

00:05:58.291 --> 00:06:01.294 line:95%,end
<i>So my girls are going to be doing</i>
<i>a hip-hop routine.</i>

00:06:01.361 --> 00:06:04.197 line:95%,end
Whatever it takes,
the Abby Lee Dance Company

00:06:04.263 --> 00:06:05.798 line:95%,end
is a full service studio.

00:06:05.865 --> 00:06:07.533 line:95%,end
And two and three and four

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:09.635 line:95%,end
and five and six and seven.

00:06:09.702 --> 00:06:11.137 line:95%,end
My girls hate hip-hop.

00:06:11.204 --> 00:06:12.739 line:95%,end
JILL: Well, how do they know
if they've never taken it?

00:06:12.805 --> 00:06:14.273 line:95%,end
I'd love to watch
Paige hip-hop, though.

00:06:14.340 --> 00:06:16.376 line:95%,end
-I have to tell you.
-Paige is funny.

00:06:16.442 --> 00:06:17.610 line:95%,end
She's like a wet noodle out there.

00:06:17.677 --> 00:06:19.645 line:95%,end
So who are you
going to ask to come?

00:06:19.712 --> 00:06:22.982 line:95%,end
I have no contacts
with any of my alumni.

00:06:23.049 --> 00:06:25.618 line:95%,end
There are so many people
who hate Abby that won't come back.

00:06:25.685 --> 00:06:27.120 line:95%,end
Like, I'm going to call them
and they're going to be like,

00:06:27.186 --> 00:06:28.821 line:95%,end
why in the world are you calling me?

00:06:28.888 --> 00:06:32.592 line:95%,end
If I can't get people to come,
it's going to be my fault.

00:06:32.658 --> 00:06:34.694 line:95%,end
And my kids are going to be put
at the bottom of the pyramid

00:06:34.761 --> 00:06:37.397 line:95%,end
once again for something I did.

00:06:37.463 --> 00:06:38.731 line:95%,end
Why didn't she just call them?

00:06:38.798 --> 00:06:41.501 line:95%,end
ABBY: Teachers told me
that the day you got that boot on,

00:06:41.567 --> 00:06:43.936 line:95%,end
you were doing cartwheels,
you were doing tinsicas,

00:06:44.003 --> 00:06:45.438 line:95%,end
you were trying to do
front walkovers in it.

00:06:45.505 --> 00:06:48.841 line:95%,end
I rode the bus home
with you two weeks ago,

00:06:48.908 --> 00:06:50.743 line:95%,end
and you were up
and down and up and down

00:06:50.810 --> 00:06:54.347 line:95%,end
and up and down that aisle
the entire time for three hours.

00:06:54.414 --> 00:06:57.750 line:95%,end
Do you like having a vacation
and not dancing?

00:06:57.817 --> 00:07:00.453 line:95%,end
I don't really look forward
to recital time or concert time.


00:07:00.520 --> 00:07:02.422 line:95%,end
-Me neither.
-Oh, really? I love it.

00:07:02.488 --> 00:07:06.292 line:95%,end
HOLLY: I find it to be an incredibly
stressful and painful experience.

00:07:06.359 --> 00:07:08.094 line:95%,end
-Me, too.
-HOLLY: It's right up there.

00:07:08.161 --> 00:07:09.829 line:95%,end
I think I'd rather have a root canal.

00:07:09.896 --> 00:07:14.333 line:5%,start
The annual ALDC concert is exhausting.

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:17.303 line:95%,end
<i>It's a time filled with highs and lows.</i>

00:07:17.370 --> 00:07:19.472 line:95%,end
We are all running on fumes.

00:07:19.539 --> 00:07:21.607 line:95%,end
I can't get up.

00:07:21.674 --> 00:07:22.909 line:95%,end
Come on.

00:07:22.975 --> 00:07:24.610 line:95%,end
JILL: It's not fair to my child.

00:07:24.677 --> 00:07:27.346 line:95%,end
She can have a duet
and win and a group

00:07:27.413 --> 00:07:28.481 line:95%,end
and be in a winning group.

00:07:28.548 --> 00:07:31.317 line:95%,end
And it has nothing to do
with her talent or her dancing.

00:07:31.384 --> 00:07:32.685 line:95%,end
-You left.
-So, we left. That's right.

00:07:32.752 --> 00:07:34.687 line:95%,end
-You left. So now you have to wait...
-And we're back.

00:07:34.754 --> 00:07:37.590 line:95%,end
...until it comes time
for auditions again to audition again.

00:07:37.657 --> 00:07:40.026 line:95%,end
Did your daughter leave the team
to go try out for cheerleading?

00:07:40.092 --> 00:07:41.961 line:95%,end
She didn't leave the team.
She asked permission to try out.

00:07:42.028 --> 00:07:46.165 line:95%,end
JILL: Oh, Kelly, you always have excuses
why your kids get what they get.

00:07:46.232 --> 00:07:48.067 line:95%,end
Going to a different studio,
Jill, is totally different.

00:07:48.134 --> 00:07:49.268 line:95%,end
-JILL: No, it's not.
-KELLY: Yes, it is.

00:07:49.335 --> 00:07:51.103 line:95%,end
-She went to a different studio...
-And she left for one week.

00:07:51.170 --> 00:07:52.805 line:95%,end
You left for months.

00:07:52.872 --> 00:07:54.207 line:95%,end
JILL: Well, it's not different.

00:07:57.009 --> 00:08:00.012 line:95%,end
(upbeat music playing)

00:08:05.885 --> 00:08:07.887 line:95%,end
Go into Studio A. Okay, babe?

00:08:07.954 --> 00:08:09.055 line:95%,end
Hey, you.

00:08:09.121 --> 00:08:10.056 line:95%,end
How are you?

00:08:10.122 --> 00:08:11.657 line:95%,end
What are you doing here?

00:08:11.724 --> 00:08:13.292 line:95%,end
You know,
I'm trying to come back.

00:08:13.359 --> 00:08:15.361 line:95%,end
Why would you do that?
Why would you put yourself through this?

00:08:15.428 --> 00:08:16.629 line:95%,end
Well, it's not me.
It's Kendall.

00:08:16.696 --> 00:08:18.698 line:95%,end
It doesn't matter.
What is she going to get out of this?

00:08:18.764 --> 00:08:20.299 line:95%,end
You know,
when I started this studio,

00:08:20.366 --> 00:08:21.868 line:95%,end
Kelly and Christi got to me.

00:08:21.934 --> 00:08:25.004 line:95%,end
You have no idea
what Melissa did to me.

00:08:25.071 --> 00:08:26.205 line:95%,end
They're never going to accept you.

00:08:26.272 --> 00:08:28.674 line:95%,end
And I don't like them,
and I don't think you like them.

00:08:28.741 --> 00:08:29.775 line:95%,end
Who are you going
to have on your side?

00:08:29.842 --> 00:08:30.977 line:95%,end
You're going to be
all by yourself.

00:08:31.043 --> 00:08:33.513 line:95%,end
You're going to just have
to defend yourself constantly

00:08:33.579 --> 00:08:35.281 line:95%,end
