00:35:01.165 --> 00:35:02.767 line:95%,end
Fabulous performance.

00:35:02.834 --> 00:35:04.469 line:95%,end
You put on a wonderful show,
Miss Abby.

00:35:04.535 --> 00:35:05.603 line:95%,end
Thank you, thank you,
thank you.

00:35:05.670 --> 00:35:07.071 line:95%,end
It was great.
They did a great job.

00:35:07.138 --> 00:35:09.307 line:95%,end
They were outstanding
from beginning to end.

00:35:09.907 --> 00:35:11.542 line:95%,end
Oh, thank you.

00:35:11.609 --> 00:35:13.244 line:95%,end
Thank you so much.

00:35:13.311 --> 00:35:15.713 line:95%,end
She really wants Kendall
on the pyramid.

00:35:15.780 --> 00:35:19.250 line:95%,end
Jill, you know, you tried the whole
gift thing with Abby before.

00:35:19.317 --> 00:35:21.819 line:95%,end
