00:35:21.886 --> 00:35:23.421 line:95%,end
<i>It's been a long few days.</i>

00:35:23.488 --> 00:35:25.690 line:95%,end
Like, you're making me
a little sick to my stomach.

00:35:25.756 --> 00:35:27.058 line:95%,end
Congratulations to you all.

00:35:27.125 --> 00:35:28.693 line:95%,end
That's what doing a show is like.

00:35:28.759 --> 00:35:31.129 line:95%,end
I think we may have gotten
some new students

00:35:31.195 --> 00:35:33.431 line:95%,end
from your performances,
so I appreciate that.

00:35:33.498 --> 00:35:37.301 line:95%,end
Remember, you're only as good
as your last performance.

