Overall, I think our girls
did a fabulous job

00:35:56.621 --> 00:35:57.622 line:95%,end
in the dance concert.

00:35:57.688 --> 00:36:00.191 line:95%,end
They had a lot on their plates,
they stepped up to the challenge,

00:36:00.258 --> 00:36:01.959 line:95%,end
and they were beautiful.

00:36:02.026 --> 00:36:04.695 line:95%,end
(applause)

00:36:06.063 --> 00:36:10.401 line:95%,end
(cheering)

00:36:19.510 --> 00:36:23.514 line:5%,start
Overall, I think the dance concert
was a success.

00:36:23.581 --> 00:36:24.415 line:5%,start
Amazing.

00:36:24.482 --> 00:36:26.717 line:95%,end
I mean, Abby has amazing kids.

00:36:26.784 --> 00:36:29.020 line:95%,end
And she's an amazing choreographer.

00:36:29.086 --> 00:36:31.389 line:95%,end
She knows how to put a show together.
That's for sure.

00:36:31.455 --> 00:36:34.125 line:95%,end
(cheering and applause)

